text: Yamauchi Shrine (山内神社) is a Shinto shrine in Kōchi, Kōchi.. It used to be a Beppyo shrine, which is a shrine with a significant history and special importance. However, it left the Beppyo list in 2013. == References == Category:Former Beppyo shrines Category:Bekkaku kanpeisha Category:1935 establishments in Japan Category:Kōchi Prefecture
title: Yamauchi Shrine
